  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4324120/extras/8dce534f827cd1f007ccb0964fa887bb.avif?t=1773921463\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Escape the Mysterious Lab</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rat #200 is a stealth point and click game where you must quietly navigate through a mysterious laboratory. Solve puzzles to acquire tools to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Be Quiet!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The scientist is always listening. Be quiet, or else…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4324120/extras/8dce534f827cd1f007ccb0964fa887bb.avif?t=1773921463\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Escape the Mysterious Lab</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rat #200 is a stealth point and click game where you must quietly navigate through a mysterious laboratory. Solve puzzles to acquire tools to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Be Quiet!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The scientist is always listening. Be quiet, or else…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
